{"type": "article", "id": 22816, "title": "带金属底座的玻璃杯", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-25T07:36:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607112003HkUD8LBj4hrFW1d2.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">伦敦设计师 Michael Anastassiades 为法国银器品牌 Puiforcat 推出了一套玻璃杯，杯子底部是尖的，需要依靠金属底座支撑，最终形成近似八角形的结构，很优雅。金属底座的光泽和玻璃杯的反光并不一样，为原本轻盈易碎的玻璃杯增加了一份厚重和精致。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112000zm6WHSs8uvIet2jb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.12179487\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112001dFUOZNm45WVePpE2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060711200212mHDX9puU8iSsew.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 250px; width: 375px; left: 566px; top: 1615px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112002DEgfsycOMwJv7B1U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607112003OF6VuWwKDivTnrfR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}